headline: Zimmer Biomet Announces Webcast and Conference Call of Third Quarter 2025 Financial Results
summary: Zimmer Biomet Holdings, Inc. (NYSE and SIX: ZBH) today announced its third quarter earnings conference call will be webcast on Wednesday, November 5, 2025 at 8:30 a.m. ET. A news release detailing the quarterly results will be made available that day at 6:30 a.m. ET.

headline: 3 Reasons to Avoid ZBH and 1 Stock to Buy Instead
summary: Over the past six months, Zimmer Biomet’s stock price fell to $99.17. Shareholders have lost 12% of their capital, which is disappointing considering the S&P 500 has climbed by 24.7%. This might have investors contemplating their next move.
